WEBVTT

00:09.501 --> 00:13.121
By the Emperor's command,
it is hereby decreed

00:13.181 --> 00:17.221
that the Minister of War, Wang Xingyi,
failed in his duties and caused harm.

00:17.771 --> 00:20.820
His position as Grand Secretary
of the Wen Yuan Pavilion is revoked.

00:20.821 --> 00:22.431
He is demoted to Police Chief

00:22.432 --> 00:24.651
of the Shengtian Prefecture
Police Office.

00:28.191 --> 00:32.101
His daughter, Wang Yingxue,
is guilty of murder.

00:32.121 --> 00:34.640
(Fangfei Pavilion)
She should've been executed immediately.

00:34.641 --> 00:37.280
But considering she has fallen ill
with madness,

00:37.281 --> 00:40.101
she is permitted to take her own life
within her household.

00:40.401 --> 00:42.021
This is the emperor's will.

00:44.041 --> 00:45.680
We thank His Majesty
for his great mercy.

00:45.681 --> 00:49.661
(Fangfei Pavilion)

00:52.961 --> 00:54.101
Ming.

00:57.041 --> 00:59.461
Ming, look at me.

01:03.401 --> 01:04.541
Ming...

01:06.441 --> 01:07.480
Ming, you're a good girl.

01:07.481 --> 01:09.981
Madam, there are so many men
in the Dou's household.

01:10.041 --> 01:12.160
Why should you be the one to do this?

01:12.161 --> 01:13.701
The imperial decree has been issued.

01:14.881 --> 01:16.701
So let me be the bad person here.

01:24.151 --> 01:25.531
Ming,

01:28.001 --> 01:29.861
look who's here.

01:36.761 --> 01:38.221
You...

01:39.971 --> 01:42.881
Are you here to laugh at me?

01:47.281 --> 01:49.381
You cursed your mother to death,

01:51.401 --> 01:53.461
then your sister.

01:54.601 --> 01:56.701
You bring nothing but bad luck.

01:57.281 --> 01:59.741
So many people wish you were dead,

02:01.321 --> 02:04.541
why don't you just grant their wish?

02:05.401 --> 02:07.461
Give me back my daughter.

02:08.561 --> 02:11.701
Bring Ming back to me.

02:13.641 --> 02:15.061
In a few days,

02:15.641 --> 02:17.341
it's my mother's birthday.

02:21.321 --> 02:24.421
Since the day
your mother hanged herself,

02:25.401 --> 02:29.821
I knew you wouldn't spare me.

02:30.841 --> 02:32.621
But I've already let you go.

02:34.281 --> 02:37.461
It's you who can't let yourself be free.

02:39.161 --> 02:41.000
Your hatred toward me runs so deep

02:41.001 --> 02:43.781
because every time you see me,

02:44.521 --> 02:46.061
you're reminded

02:46.201 --> 02:49.181
of how you drove
your best friend to suicide,

02:49.721 --> 02:51.581
how you took what was hers

02:51.881 --> 02:53.861
and ruined her happiness.

02:55.121 --> 02:56.261
You're evil.

02:56.921 --> 02:58.581
But you're still human,

02:59.241 --> 03:01.061
and your conscience haunts you.

03:02.321 --> 03:04.421
You fear the retribution that will come.

03:04.481 --> 03:05.901
Again and again,

03:06.001 --> 03:07.080
you've tried

03:07.081 --> 03:08.501
to kill me.

03:09.041 --> 03:11.741
But all you want is to escape

03:11.941 --> 03:13.301
the torment of your guilty heart.

03:13.481 --> 03:14.661
It's not true!

03:16.161 --> 03:19.560
It's natural for men to marry

03:19.561 --> 03:20.981
and take concubines.

03:21.401 --> 03:23.480
Your mother couldn't accept it!

03:23.481 --> 03:24.680
She chose to end her life!

03:24.681 --> 03:26.261
It has nothing to do with me!

03:29.121 --> 03:30.800
This is a grudge

03:30.801 --> 03:32.661
between you and my mother.

03:33.111 --> 03:35.581
Now let's

03:35.791 --> 03:37.501
settle this.

03:50.821 --> 03:52.141
Zhao Guqiu,

03:52.921 --> 03:54.541
I'm not afraid of you.

03:55.001 --> 03:56.861
I'm living well here!

04:27.321 --> 04:28.701
(What's done is done.)

04:28.711 --> 04:30.401
(Taking your life
won't change anything.)

04:30.561 --> 04:31.520
(These flower petals)

04:31.521 --> 04:33.141
(won't take your life.)

04:34.041 --> 04:35.701
(I hope this lesson)

04:35.881 --> 04:37.160
(makes you truly understand)

04:37.161 --> 04:38.941
(the pain that killed my mother)

04:39.561 --> 04:41.181
(and brings her peace.)

06:09.961 --> 06:14.200
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

06:14.201 --> 06:17.280
=Episode 24=

06:17.281 --> 06:19.461
(Dou's Residence)

06:26.921 --> 06:28.061
Ms. Longevity.

06:32.641 --> 06:33.781
Yes, Father.

06:34.921 --> 06:38.461
My marriage to Yingxue was a mistake.

06:39.721 --> 06:42.261
First, I failed you and your mother,

06:42.801 --> 06:46.541
Later, I failed her and Ming.

06:47.641 --> 06:49.541
Ming had a kind heart.

06:50.041 --> 06:51.821
She shouldn't have such an ending.

06:52.521 --> 06:55.621
She suffered from our broken marriage,

06:56.121 --> 06:58.261
which led her to fall blindly into love.

06:58.521 --> 06:59.781
I often wonder

07:00.841 --> 07:03.341
where I went wrong.

07:04.081 --> 07:07.421
Maybe I shouldn't have entered
the official world,

07:08.081 --> 07:12.061
or maybe I should never
have left the capital.

07:13.121 --> 07:14.261
If I hadn't,

07:15.441 --> 07:17.781
I'd be happily admiring

07:18.481 --> 07:20.621
the magnolia flowers blooming now.

07:24.121 --> 07:26.021
What's done is done.

07:28.001 --> 07:29.581
But unfortunately,

07:30.201 --> 07:32.581
I'm forever stuck in the past.

07:34.601 --> 07:36.141
The fact that you came to see me,

07:36.761 --> 07:38.821
I feel much better now.

07:39.681 --> 07:41.541
But after everything that happened,

07:41.721 --> 07:43.421
I want to tell you something.

07:46.361 --> 07:48.821
Seize the opportunity
while it's still available.

07:49.321 --> 07:50.661
Cherish your loved ones,

07:51.841 --> 07:53.541
so you don't regret it

07:55.521 --> 07:57.021
like I do.

08:19.601 --> 08:21.101
When did you arrive?

08:25.401 --> 08:26.541
I was already here

08:27.921 --> 08:29.981
when you entered Wang Yingxue's room.

08:31.061 --> 08:31.920
This is a grudge

08:31.921 --> 08:33.741
between you and my mother.

08:34.641 --> 08:38.021
Now let's settle this.

08:38.881 --> 08:40.701
It's such a pity for Ming.

08:41.961 --> 08:43.341
The more meaningful something is,

08:43.721 --> 08:45.941
the more strength is needed
to protect it.

08:46.661 --> 08:47.801
Ms. Longevity,

08:48.121 --> 08:49.741
I will protect you

08:50.361 --> 08:51.781
and keep you safe.

08:53.601 --> 08:54.741
I know you will.

08:55.561 --> 08:56.701
Let's go home.

08:57.081 --> 08:58.821
Yes, let's go home.

09:02.861 --> 09:04.000
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

09:04.001 --> 09:05.440
The Duke of Jining's Residence
has been confiscated,

09:05.441 --> 09:06.901
and he's been demoted to a commoner.

09:08.321 --> 09:09.160
Do you want it?

09:09.161 --> 09:10.280
Sir!

09:10.281 --> 09:11.421
Sir!

09:12.041 --> 09:13.541
- Catch!
- Give it to me.

09:14.121 --> 09:15.661
Sir, return the portrait to me.

09:15.721 --> 09:16.861
Get off me!

09:19.281 --> 09:22.280
With so many valuables,
why would you want this painting?

09:22.281 --> 09:24.661
Why? Is this a treasure map?

09:26.961 --> 09:28.101
Do you want it?

09:28.521 --> 09:29.560
If you do,

09:29.561 --> 09:32.820
kowtow three times on your knees,
and call me "Boss".

09:32.821 --> 09:34.421
Come on! Kneel!

09:35.321 --> 09:36.461
Do it.

09:38.241 --> 09:39.381
Come in.

09:40.081 --> 09:41.221
Boss.

09:41.341 --> 09:43.901
- What? I can't hear you.
- I can't hear you.

09:44.521 --> 09:45.661
Louder!

09:46.121 --> 09:47.200
Boss!

09:47.201 --> 09:49.080
Boss, return the portrait to me.

09:49.081 --> 09:50.221
Boss.

09:53.961 --> 09:55.181
Get out of here!

09:57.561 --> 09:59.471
- Leave.
- Go.

10:21.401 --> 10:23.400
(Qianqing Palace)

10:23.401 --> 10:24.240
(Revere Heaven and Ancestral Wisdom)

10:24.241 --> 10:26.941
Losing a token has caused such chaos.

10:27.601 --> 10:29.040
Shengtian Prefecture's transfer order

10:29.041 --> 10:30.741
has already reached
the Military Command.

10:30.841 --> 10:33.141
What are those useless officials doing?

10:34.441 --> 10:36.680
Your Majesty,
I failed to manage my household properly

10:36.681 --> 10:38.021
and caused this disaster.

10:38.041 --> 10:39.541
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

10:40.361 --> 10:43.261
Stop taking all the blame.

10:43.321 --> 10:45.781
It was the negligence
of the capital's defense.

10:46.321 --> 10:47.861
Your family's issues

10:48.321 --> 10:50.341
wouldn't stir up any trouble.

10:50.441 --> 10:51.400
Thank you, Your Majesty.

10:51.401 --> 10:53.520
I will immediately coordinate
with the Six Ministries

10:53.521 --> 10:55.120
and Censorate officials

10:55.121 --> 10:56.661
to thoroughly investigate this

10:56.681 --> 10:59.360
and report the details
to the Grand Secretariat

10:59.361 --> 11:01.141
for Your Majesty's decision.

11:03.481 --> 11:04.621
Approved.

11:06.601 --> 11:08.520
The Duke of Ying has kept

11:08.521 --> 11:10.061
the southern city safe.

11:10.361 --> 11:11.781
The Song Family

11:12.281 --> 11:14.261
hasn't disappointed me.

11:15.521 --> 11:16.640
Yantang,

11:16.641 --> 11:18.301
you still need to help

11:18.921 --> 11:20.421
with the aftermath.

11:23.041 --> 11:24.731
The Duke of Ying guarded
the southern city

11:24.881 --> 11:27.861
and still had his personal guards assist
my family in fighting the enemies.

11:28.801 --> 11:30.781
His attention to detail is admirable.

11:31.521 --> 11:34.221
I should learn from him.

11:36.001 --> 11:38.821
Handling the current disaster
is a pressing matter.

11:38.921 --> 11:41.741
Eradicating the bandits
is a long-term plan.

11:42.161 --> 11:44.560
I am willing
to relieve Your Majesty's worries

11:44.561 --> 11:47.381
by leading troops
to eliminate this threat.

11:49.241 --> 11:50.381
Your Majesty,

11:50.501 --> 11:53.501
the bandits are desperate but cunning.

11:53.561 --> 11:55.861
The Duke of Ying hasn't fought
in a while.

11:56.241 --> 11:57.381
I suggest

11:57.641 --> 12:00.500
letting Lord Song lead the troops,

12:00.501 --> 12:02.581
and I'll support him

12:02.841 --> 12:05.021
with strategy.

12:05.321 --> 12:06.461
Very well.

12:07.291 --> 12:10.541
Song Yichun will temporarily command
the Military Command of the Five Wards

12:10.601 --> 12:12.341
and handle the capital's aftermath.

12:12.501 --> 12:15.320
Yantang will lead the Imperial Guard
and three thousand elite soldiers.

12:15.321 --> 12:16.660
You will depart in three days.

12:16.661 --> 12:18.661
Shishu will act as the Minister of War

12:18.781 --> 12:20.261
and coordinate reinforcements.

12:20.721 --> 12:22.701
The bandits must be eradicated

12:23.481 --> 12:25.901
before you return to the capital.

12:26.171 --> 12:27.901
We shall obey your command,
Your Majesty.

12:28.041 --> 12:29.080
(Lu's Dental Clinic)

12:29.081 --> 12:31.501
These bandits have burned half
of the northern city.

12:31.761 --> 12:34.980
As long as Song Mo investigates
by following the bandits' trail,

12:34.981 --> 12:37.511
he will find something suspicious.

12:38.201 --> 12:40.821
Why not let him go after the bandits

12:41.241 --> 12:42.861
and I'll support from behind.

12:44.081 --> 12:46.101
Even if there's news,

12:46.481 --> 12:48.701
it won't reach the emperor.

12:51.441 --> 12:53.261
You truly have

12:53.521 --> 12:55.141
a great foresight.

12:55.721 --> 12:58.581
No matter how he investigates,

12:58.721 --> 13:00.181
we have nothing to fear.

13:05.521 --> 13:08.141
(Peace and Prosperity)

13:23.761 --> 13:24.800
Sir,

13:24.801 --> 13:26.381
will Madam come to see you off?

13:27.881 --> 13:29.381
It's not even my first campaign.

13:29.761 --> 13:31.381
There's no need for that.

13:33.321 --> 13:34.941
Then we should set out quickly.

13:45.841 --> 13:47.241
The auspicious time is not here yet.

13:47.761 --> 13:49.061
Of course.

13:51.921 --> 13:53.061
Yantang!

14:04.961 --> 14:06.160
Didn't you say yesterday

14:06.161 --> 14:07.301
you wouldn't see me off?

14:07.881 --> 14:09.941
I'm here to see the army off.

14:12.241 --> 14:13.581
You're lying again.

14:14.701 --> 14:16.501
Then why did you come
from outside the city?

14:18.841 --> 14:19.981
Be honest now.

14:20.801 --> 14:22.190
I went to Wanfo Temple

14:22.191 --> 14:23.640
to obtain divination sticks for you.

14:23.641 --> 14:24.941
The bandits are ruthless.

14:25.361 --> 14:26.800
So you must return unharmed

14:26.801 --> 14:28.021
and victorious.

14:30.121 --> 14:31.541
Did you leave the city so early

14:32.081 --> 14:33.781
just to get these divination sticks
for me?

14:35.121 --> 14:37.501
Aren't you afraid
I might draw a bad reading?

14:38.121 --> 14:39.560
You can draw without worries.

14:39.561 --> 14:41.000
I already picked out

14:41.001 --> 14:43.581
all the bad sticks one by one,

14:43.641 --> 14:45.261
leaving only the best ones.

14:45.601 --> 14:47.681
I didn't know
such a domineering worshiper existed.

14:50.361 --> 14:53.621
(May our love endure
and stay united for a lifetime.)

14:55.441 --> 14:57.181
Heaven watches over us

14:57.401 --> 14:59.101
and Bodhisattva truly understands
my heart.

15:00.441 --> 15:03.461
May our love endure
and stay united for a lifetime.

15:03.761 --> 15:04.391
Not this one.

15:04.401 --> 15:06.211
You must draw for peace
and a smooth journey.

15:06.221 --> 15:08.181
- Draw another one.
- What's wrong with this one?

15:08.191 --> 15:10.101
I'm not drawing another one.
I want this one.

15:11.761 --> 15:12.901
My dear,

15:13.001 --> 15:15.101
do you think
this fortune will come true?

15:15.541 --> 15:16.961
Let's talk about it when you return.

15:17.301 --> 15:18.581
I don't want to wait that long.

15:19.111 --> 15:21.010
If you don't answer me,
I'll feel restless

15:21.011 --> 15:22.201
and overthink.

15:22.211 --> 15:24.160
If I'm distracted like this
on the battlefield,

15:24.161 --> 15:26.240
I might lose an arm or a leg.

15:26.241 --> 15:28.040
What if one day I lose my head?

15:28.041 --> 15:29.571
Don't say such things!

15:29.621 --> 15:30.901
You're about to march to battle.

15:30.911 --> 15:32.481
Don't you know it's a taboo to say that?

15:35.801 --> 15:37.061
So it's a promise, then?

15:37.321 --> 15:38.581
Bodhisattva is watching.

15:38.881 --> 15:40.061
So no backing out.

15:42.441 --> 15:44.501
You must return unharmed.

15:45.441 --> 15:46.581
I will wait for you.

15:56.601 --> 15:57.741
Sir!

15:58.141 --> 15:59.040
Sir,

15:59.041 --> 16:01.321
Official Dou has ordered us
to break camp and move out.

16:10.721 --> 16:11.861
Fall in!

16:12.401 --> 16:13.541
Fall in!

16:22.641 --> 16:24.141
Imperial Guards.

16:24.341 --> 16:25.661
Here!

16:25.901 --> 16:27.301
Today, we march to battle!

16:27.391 --> 16:30.781
We swear not to return
until the bandits are defeated!

16:30.841 --> 16:32.440
Wipe out the bandits!

16:32.441 --> 16:34.000
Wipe them out!

16:34.001 --> 16:35.710
Wipe them out!

16:35.711 --> 16:36.981
March!

16:39.041 --> 16:41.981
(Yongding Gate)

16:45.401 --> 16:48.061
♪The glitter of the beautiful terrace
is just a fleeting splendor♪

16:48.581 --> 16:51.251
♪The army halts at your command♪

16:51.911 --> 16:53.310
♪Bending down for a single kiss♪

16:53.311 --> 16:57.781
♪Forsaking words of farewell♪

16:58.431 --> 17:01.151
♪The golden fiery steed rides
across the vast horizon♪

17:01.681 --> 17:04.821
♪In this life, oh♪

17:05.001 --> 17:10.271
♪What is there to envy without you?♪

17:10.691 --> 17:13.200
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

17:13.201 --> 17:17.540
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

17:17.541 --> 17:24.281
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms
bloom in a single night for you♪

17:24.601 --> 17:26.011
May our love endure

17:26.741 --> 17:27.980
and stay united for a lifetime.

17:27.981 --> 17:30.711
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

17:30.891 --> 17:37.170
♪I shall hold your hand
and walk through the dust♪

17:37.171 --> 17:39.761
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

17:39.841 --> 17:42.760
(Drunken Bordello)

17:42.761 --> 17:45.421
Isn't this the Duke?

17:47.241 --> 17:49.381
Are you here for a drink today?

17:50.411 --> 17:51.551
No, thank you.

17:53.501 --> 17:56.061
You still haven't settled the debt
from your tab at our tavern.

17:56.681 --> 17:58.421
I'll pay the tab after I have money

17:59.041 --> 18:01.261
from selling my paintings.

18:01.561 --> 18:02.701
So you don't have any money?

18:03.081 --> 18:04.221
Someone!

18:05.001 --> 18:06.261
Search him for money.

18:08.841 --> 18:09.981
Wait.

18:10.161 --> 18:11.720
I have some here.

18:11.721 --> 18:12.861
Here.

18:13.001 --> 18:14.141
Here's the money.

18:21.041 --> 18:22.341
Is this all you have?

18:23.881 --> 18:25.261
Get lost, then!

18:27.481 --> 18:28.621
Leave!

18:56.561 --> 18:57.680
His Lordship?

18:57.681 --> 18:58.941
Hurry, follow him.

19:12.601 --> 19:14.621
Fancy seeing you here, Your Lordship.

19:14.761 --> 19:16.701
How did you end up
in such a miserable state?

19:19.041 --> 19:20.181
Mr. Zhou.

19:22.961 --> 19:25.901
That painting in your hand
could be worth several taels.

19:25.911 --> 19:27.040
How about selling it to me?

19:27.041 --> 19:28.400
Take it as a favor from me.

19:28.401 --> 19:29.250
Give it to me.

19:29.251 --> 19:30.280
Mr. Zhou,

19:30.281 --> 19:31.661
this painting is not for sale.

19:31.881 --> 19:34.640
Do you think it is still up to you
whether to sell it or not?

19:34.641 --> 19:35.821
- Give it to me.
- Mr. Zhou.

19:35.831 --> 19:36.600
Help me!

19:36.601 --> 19:37.611
Mr. Zhou, don't take it.

19:37.621 --> 19:38.661
Mr. Zhou!

19:39.041 --> 19:40.661
Let me go! Give it back to me!

19:40.841 --> 19:41.981
Let me go!

19:47.241 --> 19:50.261
Ah, it's the late Marchioness.

19:50.981 --> 19:52.701
She died because of you.

19:52.781 --> 19:54.941
What's the point
of keeping her painting?

19:55.541 --> 19:58.501
How about this? I'll do you a favor

19:58.841 --> 20:01.560
and burn this painting for her
in heaven.

20:01.561 --> 20:02.600
No.

20:02.601 --> 20:03.640
Mr. Zhou.

20:03.641 --> 20:04.760
Don't burn it, Mr. Zhou.

20:04.761 --> 20:05.901
Don't burn the painting.

20:06.201 --> 20:07.400
You can't burn the painting!

20:07.401 --> 20:08.581
Please!

20:08.601 --> 20:09.741
Mr. Zhou!

20:10.321 --> 20:12.320
Don't take offense
at my previous mistakes.

20:12.321 --> 20:13.410
I'll bow as an apology.

20:13.411 --> 20:14.821
I'll bow to you.

20:15.101 --> 20:17.000
- Don't burn the painting.
- Why did you do it

20:17.001 --> 20:19.421
- Please don't burn it!
- if you knew the consequences?

20:20.741 --> 20:21.760
No!

20:21.761 --> 20:22.960
No, Mr. Zhou!

20:22.961 --> 20:24.261
Mr. Zhou, I beg you.

20:25.081 --> 20:26.280
Don't burn it, Mr. Zhou!

20:26.281 --> 20:28.541
Don't burn that painting, Mr. Zhou!

20:34.331 --> 20:36.091
No!

20:36.481 --> 20:38.141
Let me go!

20:42.401 --> 20:43.541
Darn you!

20:45.281 --> 20:46.421
Beat him!

20:58.201 --> 20:59.341
Let's go.

21:11.281 --> 21:13.221
Ming, don't be sacred. It's all right.

21:28.011 --> 21:29.520
Show it to me.

21:29.521 --> 21:30.661
I want to see it.

21:31.421 --> 21:32.280
My Lord, please.

21:32.281 --> 21:33.421
I won't let you see it.

21:38.721 --> 21:39.861
Ming,

21:40.641 --> 21:42.101
I miss you so much.

21:51.201 --> 21:53.981
I knocked Zhao out
and took her place in the bridal sedan.

21:54.121 --> 21:56.640
Tomorrow, the world will surely mock me
for degrading myself

21:56.641 --> 21:58.021
and going against tradition.

21:58.401 --> 22:01.301
Will you come and visit me in my dreams?

22:02.481 --> 22:04.461
Is this the painting you did last time?

22:05.921 --> 22:07.061
Do you like it?

22:07.161 --> 22:08.301
I do.

22:12.641 --> 22:13.821
Ming...

23:17.961 --> 23:19.101
Ming.

23:21.081 --> 23:22.221
My Lord,

23:29.921 --> 23:31.181
time for your medicine.

23:32.281 --> 23:34.861
The physician already said
your cold isn't fully recovered.

23:35.201 --> 23:37.701
Yet here you are, insisting on painting.

23:40.201 --> 23:41.341
Ming,

23:44.731 --> 23:45.941
is it really you?

23:47.521 --> 23:48.821
Am I dreaming?

23:48.921 --> 23:50.061
How could you...

23:50.161 --> 23:51.981
What are you talking about?

23:52.161 --> 23:53.120
I only left

23:53.121 --> 23:54.320
for a while.

23:54.321 --> 23:55.741
What's the matter with you?

23:56.001 --> 23:57.381
Did you have a nightmare?

23:59.521 --> 24:00.661
Ming...

24:00.891 --> 24:01.800
Ming.

24:01.801 --> 24:03.091
I don't want to be apart anymore.

24:03.101 --> 24:04.361
I don't want to leave you again.

24:04.961 --> 24:06.101
Why would we be apart?

24:06.161 --> 24:07.421
I won't leave you.

24:11.201 --> 24:12.160
Ming,

24:12.161 --> 24:13.080
I'm so glad.

24:13.081 --> 24:14.381
It was only a nightmare.

24:14.881 --> 24:16.181
We won't be apart anymore.

24:25.161 --> 24:26.301
Here you go.

25:12.881 --> 25:14.861
After the imperial decree was issued,

25:15.441 --> 25:18.581
a mad sorcerer came to the household,

25:18.881 --> 25:20.421
claiming he could cure her illness.

25:21.081 --> 25:25.021
He said she only needs to bow her way up
the mountain every day.

25:25.561 --> 25:28.141
One bow after three steps
and one kowtow after nine steps

25:28.321 --> 25:30.141
while chanting scriptures
a hundred times.

25:30.721 --> 25:34.941
Only then, could Ming be spared
from the torments of hell.

25:36.841 --> 25:40.501
After she heard that,
she actually stopped acting mad

25:42.481 --> 25:44.061
and begged to come here.

25:45.841 --> 25:47.141
It seems

25:48.641 --> 25:50.381
that Mother has forgiven her.

25:51.481 --> 25:53.741
Thanks to your plea for imperial mercy,

25:53.961 --> 25:56.861
she's been allowed to spend
the rest of her days here.

25:58.681 --> 26:00.981
Consider it her way of atoning
for her sins.

26:06.321 --> 26:08.174
From the foot of the mountain
to the summit,

26:08.175 --> 26:09.560
there are over a thousand steps.

26:09.561 --> 26:12.181
Even walking up would take hours,

26:12.521 --> 26:15.221
let alone bowing every three steps
and prostrating every nine steps.

26:15.481 --> 26:16.661
How could a woman

26:16.671 --> 26:18.391
possibly complete such a task
over 999 days

26:18.401 --> 26:20.861
while enduring rain, snow, and wind?

26:22.621 --> 26:23.861
It'll be hard in her lifetime.

26:23.921 --> 26:24.880
That's the point.

26:24.881 --> 26:26.720
There's a saying in Buddhism

26:26.721 --> 26:28.120
about Avici Hell.

26:28.121 --> 26:30.080
It's the worst of the eight hell.

26:30.081 --> 26:31.541
Those who committed the gravest sins

26:31.561 --> 26:32.800
will be cast there

26:32.801 --> 26:33.840
and will never

26:33.841 --> 26:35.701
have the hope of release.

26:43.441 --> 26:44.981
When the bandits attacked the residence,

26:45.001 --> 26:46.841
I thought you only suffered
physical injuries.

26:46.861 --> 26:48.341
I didn't realize it was psychological.

26:48.441 --> 26:49.590
You're restless,

26:49.591 --> 26:52.301
sleepless, and troubled by dreams.
Am I right?

26:58.361 --> 26:59.821
There's something else.

27:00.001 --> 27:02.840
My friend's husband is away,

27:02.841 --> 27:04.101
and she keeps having nightmares.

27:04.361 --> 27:06.120
She dreamt her husband

27:06.121 --> 27:07.821
was ambushed in a forest.

27:08.721 --> 27:10.680
She came to me to interpret the dream,

27:10.681 --> 27:12.861
asking if her husband was safe.

27:13.561 --> 27:15.221
But I don't know these things.

27:18.441 --> 27:19.821
Could it be

27:21.121 --> 27:22.861
that the forest is near Jinxi?

27:31.201 --> 27:32.341
It's over.

27:32.921 --> 27:34.860
It's all over.

27:34.861 --> 27:35.760
What's wrong?

27:35.761 --> 27:36.720
It's over.

27:36.721 --> 27:38.031
Your friend's husband

27:38.041 --> 27:40.360
has fallen prey to an enemy,
with omens of blood and death.

27:40.361 --> 27:41.981
He won't live much longer.

27:46.601 --> 27:48.880
My friend also dreamt

27:48.881 --> 27:50.781
that someone was cursing her husband.

27:50.801 --> 27:53.520
He ended up with his mouth,
stomach, and heart rotting.

27:53.521 --> 27:54.661
Madam!

27:55.521 --> 27:56.781
A letter from His Lordship.

27:59.881 --> 28:01.981
Sharped-tongued but soft heart.

28:03.081 --> 28:04.781
You should be quiet.

28:08.641 --> 28:09.781
Prepare the horse!

28:10.841 --> 28:12.161
You don't need treatment anymore?

28:18.921 --> 28:20.360
The bandits broke through the siege.

28:20.361 --> 28:21.961
His Lordship was ambushed in the woods.

29:09.721 --> 29:10.941
What's the matter, my dear?

29:12.001 --> 29:12.880
I'm right here.

29:12.881 --> 29:14.021
Yantang.

29:15.761 --> 29:17.261
Your concern makes you overthink.

29:20.441 --> 29:21.581
Are you all right?

29:22.001 --> 29:23.141
I'm all right.

29:25.681 --> 29:27.981
Yan Chaoqing said
you were ambushed in the forest.

29:28.361 --> 29:29.981
I was the one who ambushed them.

29:30.161 --> 29:32.701
If I needed you to save me
from these bandits,

29:32.921 --> 29:34.861
I might as well go home
and do needlework.

29:38.481 --> 29:39.621
Enough with the nonsense.

29:39.681 --> 29:40.821
Get out of here!

29:50.041 --> 29:51.280
Even so,

29:51.281 --> 29:52.821
I did get hurt.

29:53.041 --> 29:54.421
That archer was skilled.

29:54.881 --> 29:56.741
Luckily, I had my golden silk armor.

29:57.241 --> 29:58.541
Are your hands all right?

29:58.681 --> 30:00.101
Did you get injured here?

30:01.161 --> 30:02.661
Let's head back to the camp.

30:02.761 --> 30:04.101
I'll take a look at your wounds.

30:07.601 --> 30:09.301
Massaging around the wound helps

30:09.601 --> 30:11.241
with blood circulation,

30:11.561 --> 30:13.101
which can speed up the healing.

30:16.121 --> 30:17.581
Let me see the wound.

30:18.281 --> 30:19.421
No need.

30:20.481 --> 30:21.600
It's almost healed.

30:21.601 --> 30:23.341
You were just crying out
in pain earlier.

30:23.561 --> 30:26.621
Are you afraid I'd worry
because the injury is serious?

30:27.801 --> 30:28.800
Let me see.

30:28.801 --> 30:29.800
No need, really.

30:29.801 --> 30:30.941
Let me check.

30:32.721 --> 30:33.861
What's wrong?

30:39.881 --> 30:41.301
Your injury is serious.

30:43.721 --> 30:44.861
Does it still hurt?

30:47.161 --> 30:48.301
No.

30:48.601 --> 30:49.741
It's only a minor injury.

30:51.001 --> 30:52.901
At home, no one cared if I was hurt.

30:52.961 --> 30:54.501
But seeing how you worry about me,

30:54.921 --> 30:56.701
I realize even small injuries

30:57.041 --> 30:59.101
can make you worry for a while.

30:59.121 --> 31:00.581
Who says I'm worried about you?

31:05.041 --> 31:07.021
Do you know what day it is today?

31:07.841 --> 31:09.061
Today is...

31:10.041 --> 31:11.221
Time stands still in the army.

31:11.231 --> 31:13.221
Today is your birthday.

31:21.241 --> 31:22.421
Here's some birthday noodles.

31:23.201 --> 31:24.501
Happy birthday.

31:27.001 --> 31:29.301
You remembered my birthday?

31:29.641 --> 31:30.821
Of course, I do.

31:40.561 --> 31:41.701
Thank you, my dear.

31:43.281 --> 31:44.421
Have a taste.

31:46.961 --> 31:48.581
Slowly.

31:48.921 --> 31:50.061
Is it delicious?

31:51.841 --> 31:53.141
Since you made it,

31:53.361 --> 31:54.501
it's delicious.

32:00.281 --> 32:03.661
Can you fulfill

32:03.761 --> 32:05.421
my birthday wish today?

32:06.841 --> 32:07.981
What is it?

32:09.041 --> 32:10.221
Don't be angry.

32:10.761 --> 32:11.901
All right.

32:33.081 --> 32:34.221
General!

32:39.561 --> 32:41.501
You better say something useful.

32:42.161 --> 32:43.581
- Or else...
- I know.

32:44.001 --> 32:45.141
Running in laps.

32:45.881 --> 32:47.021
So, what is it?

32:48.441 --> 32:49.560
General.

32:49.561 --> 32:51.781
The refugees we saved
from the bandits have woken up.

32:51.801 --> 32:54.381
They said they want to thank you.

32:54.761 --> 32:55.901
All right.

33:00.841 --> 33:02.021
Why are you still here?

33:23.401 --> 33:25.280
Thank you for saving my son and I.

33:25.281 --> 33:26.581
Please get up.

33:27.881 --> 33:30.221
It was no trouble at all.

33:30.251 --> 33:32.021
Where are you from?

33:32.361 --> 33:34.221
My husband is a general.

33:34.441 --> 33:36.341
He can ask someone to take you home.

33:36.401 --> 33:37.901
Thank you, Madam.

33:38.241 --> 33:41.200
Our village was burned down by bandits.

33:41.201 --> 33:43.061
We have no home anymore.

33:44.241 --> 33:46.821
We are on our way to the capital
to find my sister.

33:47.481 --> 33:49.620
Where does your sister live
in the capital?

33:49.621 --> 33:51.421
My eldest daughter lives there.

33:51.721 --> 33:53.861
But we don't know where exactly.

33:54.721 --> 33:56.261
The capital is so big

33:56.721 --> 34:00.061
and we don't know how to find her.

34:03.401 --> 34:04.541
Madam,

34:04.601 --> 34:06.461
I have a place in the capital

34:06.721 --> 34:08.941
that sells stationery.

34:09.241 --> 34:10.781
If you don't mind,

34:11.241 --> 34:13.160
you can stay there

34:13.161 --> 34:14.341
for now

34:14.561 --> 34:16.501
and look for your daughter from there.

34:16.601 --> 34:18.520
Thank you so much, Madam.

34:18.521 --> 34:20.720
Can, kneel and thank Madam.

34:20.721 --> 34:22.541
- Get up.
- Please get up.

34:24.081 --> 34:26.461
Thank you very much.

34:30.841 --> 34:32.421
Madam! Madam!

34:33.641 --> 34:37.000
Madam, my mother wants you
to have this hairpin.

34:37.001 --> 34:38.181
Thank you.

34:39.161 --> 34:40.301
I cannot accept this.

34:45.001 --> 34:46.141
General!

34:46.481 --> 34:47.621
What is it?

34:48.381 --> 34:51.000
General, we have received a report
from Guanghe Tower in the city.

34:51.001 --> 34:52.141
What is it about?

34:52.321 --> 34:54.621
In summary, we won.

34:54.741 --> 34:56.421
But there are many rumors in court.

34:56.431 --> 34:59.331
They say you are ambitious and don't follow
the Ministry of War's orders.

34:59.341 --> 35:01.520
They also say the bandits' raid

35:01.521 --> 35:03.220
was because Madam flaunted her dowry,

35:03.221 --> 35:04.400
which made the bandits envious

35:04.401 --> 35:05.981
and caused trouble for the people.

35:06.721 --> 35:08.301
Being wealthy brings trouble.

35:08.801 --> 35:09.800
What did His Majesty say?

35:09.801 --> 35:11.600
Official Dou Shishu defended you a bit.

35:11.601 --> 35:13.141
His Majesty promoted him to a deputy

35:13.281 --> 35:15.861
but didn't mention any rewards for you.

35:16.161 --> 35:17.501
Giving backhanded remarks

35:17.921 --> 35:19.541
is what my Fifth Uncle is good at.

35:20.041 --> 35:21.320
He likely spread rumors

35:21.321 --> 35:22.941
about you being ambitious

35:23.841 --> 35:26.341
to make His Majesty wary
of your independence.

35:28.081 --> 35:29.501
The bandit chaos in the capital!

35:29.801 --> 35:31.901
Two hundred thirty-nine bandits

35:32.041 --> 35:33.581
were executed.

35:33.641 --> 35:35.181
In the campaign to eliminate bandits,

35:35.321 --> 35:37.141
seven major gangs
from the three provinces,

35:37.281 --> 35:41.031
totaling 8,000 bandits who had been
terrorizing the outskirts of the capital,

35:41.121 --> 35:43.301
have all been either killed or captured!

35:43.641 --> 35:46.920
If anyone dares
to cause more trouble in the capital

35:46.921 --> 35:48.821
and harm the people in the future,

35:48.881 --> 35:50.781
their bodies will be displayed
on the city walls

35:50.881 --> 35:52.341
for the birds

35:52.601 --> 35:54.080
as a warning to others!

35:54.081 --> 35:58.761
- Good!
- Well said!

35:58.771 --> 36:00.511
I have arranged for prayers
at Wanfo Temple

36:00.521 --> 36:03.141
for the suffering people.

36:03.761 --> 36:05.061
From today,

36:05.661 --> 36:07.821
all celebrations and feasts
are suspended for a month

36:08.161 --> 36:09.741
in honor of the dead.

36:11.081 --> 36:12.501
For those affected,

36:12.601 --> 36:15.240
Zhaowen Bookstore and Miao's Family Shop

36:15.241 --> 36:17.421
have prepared food and medicine.

36:17.801 --> 36:20.301
They will be given out
for free for three days.

36:23.481 --> 36:30.101
- Wonderful!
- Great!

36:30.381 --> 36:32.630
Song Mo is winning the hearts
of people in the capital.

36:32.631 --> 36:34.661
You should deprive him of his power

36:34.721 --> 36:35.941
as a warning.

36:37.121 --> 36:38.200
Your Majesty.

36:38.201 --> 36:39.680
But Lord Song's wife said

36:39.681 --> 36:44.021
that giving out medicine and food is Your
Majesty's grace and the court's gesture.

36:44.401 --> 36:46.061
Using kindness and authority

36:46.961 --> 36:48.741
to eliminate the reputation
of being brutal.

36:49.871 --> 36:51.841
It also ends rumors and public anger

36:52.281 --> 36:54.901
as well as giving me a face.

36:55.481 --> 36:56.560
But

36:56.561 --> 37:00.261
this is clearly just flattery
and scheming.

37:05.521 --> 37:08.421
If you could learn
how to flatter and scheme like this,

37:08.951 --> 37:10.731
I'd be at ease.

37:14.131 --> 37:17.501
What about the feast for Lord Song?

37:17.761 --> 37:19.341
It shouldn't have been held.

37:21.881 --> 37:23.000
As mentioned earlier,

37:23.001 --> 37:25.621
the civil and military officials
lack vigilance.

37:25.721 --> 37:27.661
Only Yantang was thoughtful.

37:29.801 --> 37:30.960
Issue my decree.

37:30.961 --> 37:33.351
Over a thousand people
in the capital were killed or injured.

37:33.361 --> 37:34.861
According to the mourning regulations,

37:35.241 --> 37:37.861
from the palace to the officials,

37:38.161 --> 37:40.301
all celebrations will be banned
for a month.

37:41.281 --> 37:42.421
Yes, Your Majesty.

37:45.601 --> 37:46.741
Father,

37:47.201 --> 37:49.061
why did you bring me here?

37:49.321 --> 37:50.560
I have found

37:50.561 --> 37:52.850
the best teacher in the world
to teach you music and arts.

37:52.851 --> 37:55.161
It's also to celebrate your birthday.

37:55.361 --> 37:56.501
Follow me.

38:09.641 --> 38:10.781
Come inside.

38:14.401 --> 38:15.741
Come.

38:22.801 --> 38:23.941
Shuyao.

38:41.781 --> 38:42.961
Han.

38:47.041 --> 38:48.181
A gift for you.

38:48.961 --> 38:50.101
May it keep you safe.

38:51.361 --> 38:52.501
Father.

38:54.641 --> 38:55.781
Han.

38:56.121 --> 38:57.261
All these years,

38:57.361 --> 38:59.501
the birthday gifts I delivered to you

39:01.081 --> 39:04.781
were personally made by her.

39:10.441 --> 39:12.421
Do you understand her intention?

39:20.401 --> 39:21.781
I don't understand anything.

39:23.921 --> 39:25.061
Han.

39:27.721 --> 39:28.861
Han!

39:44.201 --> 39:45.341
Han.

39:45.961 --> 39:47.101
Mo?

39:49.801 --> 39:50.941
What happened to your eyes?

39:51.041 --> 39:52.341
Were they irritated by the smoke?

39:53.961 --> 39:55.080
I'm fine, Mo.

39:55.081 --> 39:56.221
What brings you here?

39:57.521 --> 39:59.501
Your cat ran to Yizhi Hall again.

39:59.961 --> 40:01.101
I caught it for you.

40:02.641 --> 40:03.981
It loves to run around.

40:05.681 --> 40:06.821
What are you burning?

40:08.921 --> 40:10.320
I needed a pendant for my belt.

40:10.321 --> 40:11.981
So I had a maid to make one.

40:12.001 --> 40:13.080
It didn't turn out well.

40:13.081 --> 40:14.221
So I burned it.

40:23.281 --> 40:24.421
Sir,

40:24.481 --> 40:26.000
General Yan and Officer Chen are here.

40:26.001 --> 40:27.181
They said it was urgent.

40:28.041 --> 40:29.520
Let them wait in the front hall.

40:29.521 --> 40:31.341
- Yes, sir.
- Officer Chen?

40:31.681 --> 40:33.320
He is an undercover agent

40:33.321 --> 40:35.821
I planted in the Northern Pacification
Bureau, named Chen Jia.

40:38.241 --> 40:39.461
(Chen Jia?)

40:46.681 --> 40:48.061
I'll make you pay!

40:55.561 --> 40:57.541
Can I listen to your conversation?

41:05.401 --> 41:07.461
- Greetings, My Lord.
- Good evening, Your Lordship.

41:07.481 --> 41:09.931
We've looked into the house
in the northern part of the city.

41:09.961 --> 41:11.671
The original owner registered
under a false name.

41:11.681 --> 41:14.101
The woman living there now
is only known as Li.

41:14.201 --> 41:15.901
She enjoys playing music.

41:16.041 --> 41:17.341
I matched her appearance,

41:17.351 --> 41:19.121
features, and preferences
with the portrait.

41:19.131 --> 41:21.821
I suspect she was a former official courtesan
from the Music Office,

41:21.831 --> 41:23.981
who was reported dead early on,

41:24.361 --> 41:25.501
named Li Yaoniang.

41:25.521 --> 41:26.741
Li Yaoniang?

41:27.361 --> 41:28.781
How long has she been living there?

41:29.001 --> 41:30.181
Twenty years.

41:30.911 --> 41:33.981
Neighbors say a sedan often stops
at the back door at night.

41:34.251 --> 41:36.281
I've also matched
the appearance with the portrait.

41:36.291 --> 41:38.141
It's a sedan
from the Duke of Ying's Residence.

41:46.561 --> 41:48.781
Don't worry about it, continue.

41:48.961 --> 41:50.680
I also found the old neighbors nearby

41:50.681 --> 41:51.821
and verified it.

41:55.321 --> 41:56.741
He never took concubines,

41:57.681 --> 42:00.101
and I thought he was loyal to Mother.

42:00.921 --> 42:02.701
It turns out
he had secretly kept a mistress.

42:03.281 --> 42:04.400
My Lord,

42:04.401 --> 42:05.981
how could the Duke of Ying alone rescue

42:06.321 --> 42:08.480
and hide a convicted woman

42:08.481 --> 42:10.061
for twenty years

42:10.201 --> 42:11.821
under the nose of the Duchess?

42:11.921 --> 42:13.381
It's not easy.

42:13.521 --> 42:15.480
Who does she usually associate with?

42:15.481 --> 42:16.901
She rarely goes out.

42:16.921 --> 42:19.000
She would only visit Wanfo Temple
at the beginning and fifteenth

42:19.001 --> 42:21.131
of each month to burn incense
and listen to scriptures.

42:21.141 --> 42:22.861
The abbot there is familiar with her.

42:24.681 --> 42:25.821
Keep following this lead.

42:27.041 --> 42:28.181
Yes, sir.

42:38.681 --> 42:39.920
We'll split up to investigate.

42:39.921 --> 42:41.181
I'll go to Wanfo Temple.

42:42.441 --> 42:43.581
All right.

42:46.081 --> 42:47.861
No matter what happens,

42:48.321 --> 42:49.461
don't forget

42:49.921 --> 42:51.301
that you still have me.

43:04.011 --> 43:06.381
Why are you so foolish?

43:34.081 --> 43:35.701
Licorice-preserved fruit clashes

43:35.761 --> 43:38.141
with the euphorbia
in Mother's prescription.

43:38.161 --> 43:40.320
You caused her death!

43:40.321 --> 43:42.381
Giving birth to you with her

43:42.841 --> 43:45.661
was the greatest regret of my life!

43:46.281 --> 43:47.421
Yantang!

43:48.521 --> 43:52.961
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

43:53.241 --> 43:56.421
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:57.001 --> 44:00.581
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:00.681 --> 44:06.581
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:06.921 --> 44:08.240
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

44:08.241 --> 44:11.320
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

44:11.321 --> 44:15.181
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

44:15.241 --> 44:19.480
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

44:19.481 --> 44:22.040
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

44:22.041 --> 44:23.320
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

44:23.321 --> 44:26.360
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

44:26.361 --> 44:30.520
♪Would you take away the weight
of the past?♪

44:30.521 --> 44:32.520
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

44:32.521 --> 44:35.720
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:35.721 --> 44:41.861
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:43.841 --> 44:50.741
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves,
moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:51.201 --> 44:58.421
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:58.721 --> 45:01.941
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

45:02.521 --> 45:06.101
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

45:06.201 --> 45:12.101
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

45:12.721 --> 45:14.000
♪In this chaotic world♪

45:14.001 --> 45:16.960
♪Only love lasts♪

45:16.961 --> 45:20.701
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

45:20.881 --> 45:25.120
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

45:25.121 --> 45:27.720
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

45:27.721 --> 45:28.920
♪My heart feels empty♪

45:28.921 --> 45:31.840
♪But I can hear your voice♪

45:31.841 --> 45:36.120
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

45:36.121 --> 45:38.541
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

45:38.761 --> 45:39.600
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:39.601 --> 45:40.520
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:40.521 --> 45:41.520
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

45:41.521 --> 45:47.621
♪Together,
we'll make every moment count♪
